title: Amount of Chickens to Collect
body:
The FUCD vault now has 2.39 ETH and each chicken will cost 0.042 WETH. There will be some Ethereum gas fees to bridge ETH into WETH. 0.18 ETH will be reserved for those fees. And there will be minimum fees in Matic to transfer and mint chickens in Polygon. 0.01 ETH converted to Matic will be reserved for those gas fees.

FUCD holders have several choices for the amount of chickens hunters will attempt to mint:

50 chickens - 2.1 ETH
40 chickens - 1.68 ETH
30 chickens - 1.26 ETH
20 chickens - 0.84 ETH

Less than the amounts above will severely lower the ROI. Please vote for the preferred amount you would like FUCDAO to attempt to mint.
